milies<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Light And Loving It! A Kitchen Design For All Seasons<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Light and appealing, this kitchen\u2019s interiors have a tasteful modern touch to them. The intelligent use of plants and exotic furniture is ideal for any middle-class family in India. The pop of light pink on the curtains adds a charismatic effect. This is indeed a visual representation of the quote: \u201cThe beauty of simplicity surpasses the need for things.\u201d This is proof that you don\u2019t need fancy stuff to spruce up your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-decor-decorating-ideas\/\">kitchen decor<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192158\/all-season-best-kitchen-design-for-a-middle-class.jpg\" alt=\"All season-best kitchen design for a middle class with a pop of light pink on the curtains adds a charismatic effect.\" class=\"wp-image-24153\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192158\/all-season-best-kitchen-design-for-a-middle-class.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192158\/all-season-best-kitchen-design-for-a-middle-class-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192158\/all-season-best-kitchen-design-for-a-middle-class-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192158\/all-season-best-kitchen-design-for-a-middle-class-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Cook with a view in this well-ventilated modern kitchen that doesn\u2019t hurt your budget<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wooden Furnishings That Create An Unearthly Glow<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If we say you don&#8217;t need tons of money for a kitchen decor like this, would you believe us? Well, you should and must! The impeccable use of wooden furnishing along with the fresh white radiates an unearthly glow. The fantastic mix of nudes and pop of bright colours is a delight to the eyes. Don\u2019t over-accessorise; keep it simple like uncarved wood!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192352\/wooden-furnishing-kitchen-design-for-middle-class-family.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen design for a middle-class family with wooden furnishing looks delight to the eyes.\" class=\"wp-image-24162\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192352\/wooden-furnishing-kitchen-design-for-middle-class-family.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192352\/wooden-furnishing-kitchen-design-for-middle-class-family-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192352\/wooden-furnishing-kitchen-design-for-middle-class-family-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192352\/wooden-furnishing-kitchen-design-for-middle-class-family-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Looking for the spacious feel on a budget? You got that<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Brown And White Combination That Looks Too Good To Be True<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The colour white is timeless. Take a look at the image \u2014 the mesmerising effect of the brown among the ethereal white seems too good to be true! Invest in some tools and chic cabinet hardware, and you can pull this look off just as it is! This kitchen decor isn\u2019t expensive at all and is the perfect design for a small Indian kitchen for a middle-class family.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192212\/beautiful-modern-kitchen-design-for-middle-class.jpg\" alt=\"Beautiful modern kitchen design for the middle class in u-shaped with brown and white combination\" class=\"wp-image-24154\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192212\/beautiful-modern-kitchen-design-for-middle-class.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192212\/beautiful-modern-kitchen-design-for-middle-class-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192212\/beautiful-modern-kitchen-design-for-middle-class-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/11192212\/beautiful-modern-kitchen-design-for-middle-class-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The white will calm your senses while you cook in this mesmerising white kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The kitchen is not just a place for cooking; it\u2019s a place for relaxing, gossiping and sharing. The kitchen is known as the heart of a home \u2014 and renovating it is the best way to do away with the stress of everyday life. To modify your kitchen, you don\u2019t need to knock down all the walls. Duh! All you need is the right mix of accessories \u2014 whether it is a stylish wall clock, a unique set of stools, artwork or lighting, and you can transform your kitchen on a low budget.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With some of the ideas that we have shared above, you can boost your kitchen\u2019s visual appeal and fall in love with your space even more!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We love to hear from you! Drop us some love in the comments below!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Have any questions? We answer with a cheeky smile here.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/budget-friendly-modular-kitchen-design-ideas\/\">Budget Friendly Modular Kitchen Design Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/small-kitchen-organisation-on-budget\/\">Small Kitchen Organisation On Budget<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Modular Kitchens At Best Prices<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our kitchen experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021